_sText:
Welcome!
==================
This map was created for my own server. I decided to publish, and here you are.

SPECS:
------------------

- 32 spawns
- surf ramps
- anti-roof and anti-noob room
- 2 bomb sites
- 4 secrets
- new textures and skybox

#### RECOMMENDED

It's recommended to use bhop boost on your server, otherwise people will have a hard time surfing and going to the upper level again.

**Happy surfing.**
